725455f-a.title: Queens: 54th Street - Roosevelt Avenue
725455f-a.text:
P,4th Street (foreground, unpaved), between Roosevelt Ave. (left) and Skillman Ave.(right), showing in the foreground the G. Susdorff house from 1860-1873. It was gone in April 1925. In the background are homes
on 52nd Street.
March 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
